---
Format Starlark policy files using ruff

Usage: fmt [OPTIONS] [FILES]...

Arguments:
  [FILES]...  Policy files to format (default: all active policy files)

Options:
      --check  Check formatting without modifying files (exit 1 if unformatted)
  -h, --help   Print help
